{"tid":871650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人命不值錢？解放軍手牽手　進地雷區用腳掃雷","createTime":"2018-10-22T06:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T06:21:06.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"efac404c472a0954ff5fb3b1d483606750106da1","tid":871650,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:21:02.000Z","msg":"中國央視網10月18日，分享士兵手牽手進地雷區驗收掃雷成果的影片，宣稱是「大無畏的革命精神」，讓中國網友吐槽「這價值觀有毛病」、「這不叫勇氣自信，叫草菅人命」、「領導不把士兵當人」。<br />\n<br />\n據《自由亞洲電台》報導，從央視網的影片可看到，解放軍們手牽手唱著歌，走入中越邊境的地雷區，官方也宣，解放軍們無謂生死、在用腳查探有否殘餘地雷，現在沒有哪個國家的軍隊，有如此的勇氣和自信。<br />\n<br />\n觀察人士傅先生指出，這舉動反映軍隊並沒有把士兵的生命當作一回事，「就是想通過這種（行動），來煽動一個所謂的愛國情結，就跟那個抗洪搶險士兵上去肉搏是一個理。完全沒有理性、沒有邏輯。」<br />\n  <br />\n影片曝光後，中國網友也紛紛留言「這是在拿年輕的生命開玩笑吧」、「叫隻豬上去跑不就好了」、「拿生並當兒戲」、「人多也不能這樣操作」、「我們繳了稅，買台排雷車好嗎」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181021/640_3a26dd4b67899f3aa6c6c3ec811826c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181021%2F640_3a26dd4b67899f3aa6c6c3ec811826c6.jpg&h=7f2a7863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181021/640_2bb82b45af1a6a6397fec45cfc7b7b29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181021%2F640_2bb82b45af1a6a6397fec45cfc7b7b29.jpg&h=4443d5cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181021/640_0fdadd30ae8ea57622cab0d7804d98ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181021%2F640_0fdadd30ae8ea57622cab0d7804d98ac.jpg&h=fffddaa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181021/1451506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181021%2F1451506&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=bcb255f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181021%2F1451506&h=96386736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181021/1451506</a>"},{"pid":"da2dace7f5c53d4f1d59f39b4d99b2bc7b64009a","tid":871650,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>有解放軍官兵處理手榴彈期間發生爆炸 當場昏迷</strong><br />\n<br />\n解放軍官兵近日在中越邊境雲南段，展開掃雷行動。有官兵處理一枚手榴彈期間發生爆炸，當場昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n由央視網的片段見到，官兵手牽手築成人鏈，唱著軍歌執行任務，期間一名處理一枚遺留的手榴彈時，手榴彈突然爆炸，身穿保護衣的官兵全身多處受傷，傷勢嚴重，當場昏迷，先送到附近縣醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n部隊醫院之後抽調包括外科、骨科、眼科及燒傷科等專家，組成搶救小組為他緊急治療，目前已脫離生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5bcb18f3e60383365be49cfa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5bcb18f3e60383365be49cfa%2F&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7a212b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5bcb18f3e60383365be49cfa/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}